metadata.name: A w a k e n i n g
metadata.description:
How Camila arrived on Mars is unknown to anyone. 

You can see how she opens her eyes for the first time on a planet far from Earth. 

Try to imagine the thoughts that visit her. What do you think the first man thinks when he opens his eyes and sees Mars?

The first and only shot of the first and so far only awakening of man on this planet.


1 of 7 NFTs in the collection, 1 / 1
